movies.title: Sons of Anarchy
movies.overview: An adrenalized drama with darkly comedic undertones that explores a notorious outlaw motorcycle club’s (MC) desire to protect its livelihood while ensuring that their simple, sheltered town of Charming, California remains exactly that, charming. The MC must confront threats from drug dealers, corporate developers, and overzealous law officers. Behind the MC’s familial lifestyle and legally thriving automotive shop is a ruthless and illegal arms business driven by the seduction of money, power, and blood.

f5889316-9151-4dad-9ad7-00447168387c.title: Papa's Goods
f5889316-9151-4dad-9ad7-00447168387c.overview: Ghosts loom large as Jax makes the final moves to fulfill his father's legacy.

29f5a2bc-22d6-49b4-8fc5-0b1a7db0ec6a.title: Red Rose
29f5a2bc-22d6-49b4-8fc5-0b1a7db0ec6a.overview: With tensions mounting and truths finally revealed, Jax must make the ultimate decision.

0e597278-03c7-4a4b-ae0a-c92594841028.overview: The SOA organization bears down on SAMCRO and Jax comes face to face with an ugly truth.

685e6720-8360-4727-8c45-3fda2ad8aab9.title: Faith and Despondency
685e6720-8360-4727-8c45-3fda2ad8aab9.overview: SAMCRO members fall in love, but death is in the air.

87ac732d-47e9-4d04-b37f-2df6ad8c7737.overview: A past effort to help one ally leads to trouble with another.

9d392e32-5262-43bc-b318-46daf3a0a4ca.overview: SAMCRO exploits an opportunity to secure an important alliance.

c2e08ec3-3fc4-49ee-ac51-29ca6a3599bd.overview: SAMCRO solicits help from another Charter to get a messy job done.

b602d1c7-7e65-40d5-836e-1500ec692017.overview: The ramifications of Jax’s choices put his club and family in jeopardy.

4d4cfc6f-8e8d-476a-84b9-91d09a98c259.overview: As the dust beings to settle Jax’s world is suddenly turned upside down.

ef146dd3-ef0a-4ba5-a2d2-6f3d7ac8f834.overview: Jax learns new secrets that turn his world sideways.

99c85ad8-990e-4158-9e4d-cef3ac08d43d.overview: Triggers are pulled that strengthen the MC, but also threaten to destroy it.

00ac39cd-6032-4985-99f7-8bd294945444.overview: Jax and the MC must confront their past and choose their future.

f93e1be4-2f2c-4664-816f-859c0165013e.overview: The club is forced to make an uneasy alliance with unforeseen consequences.

ff07ae1e-07e6-46b2-a67c-7daf67565ff2.title: Wolfsangel
ff07ae1e-07e6-46b2-a67c-7daf67565ff2.overview: An attack at the compound leads SOA to seek revenge.

1cb02a0f-e2b4-405e-91f6-ca0f268f7b04.overview: Jax secures a new alliance for the club while Clay makes moves inside for protection.

d0b7dec6-a169-49a4-b686-fce166431e44.overview: Jax deals with collateral damage as external pressure continue to stack up against SAMCRO.

cc08ca02-78b7-4113-b3ad-da66589b34c6.title: Straw
cc08ca02-78b7-4113-b3ad-da66589b34c6.overview: As Jax continues to push the club into more legitimate businesses he can’t escape the sins of SAMCRO’s past.

2dce453c-1c72-4284-a766-e5c3c9cf5cac.title: Darthy
2dce453c-1c72-4284-a766-e5c3c9cf5cac.overview: Jax makes arrangements to take the club in a different direction.

8872d6f4-931c-4548-bbbe-3c22aedeed96.overview: Jax scrambles to put his affairs in order, while Nero handles business with his old crew.

0cc3b63a-e981-4431-ae79-3a6602eb4cf2.title: Crucifixed
0cc3b63a-e981-4431-ae79-3a6602eb4cf2.overview: Anticipating backlash, Jax goes into high gear with his own agenda.

1a5860e4-3843-486b-9021-dfae24a9acf6.title: Andare Pescare
1a5860e4-3843-486b-9021-dfae24a9acf6.overview: Jax gets closer to the truth but there are still obstacles in his way.

5c316495-ecc1-4a4d-bc88-3102d11c7541.title: Ablation
5c316495-ecc1-4a4d-bc88-3102d11c7541.overview: Alliances are tested, while bonds are broken.

fd6bbf00-e258-480c-9e7c-14f3127e6c03.title: Toad's Wild Ride
fd6bbf00-e258-480c-9e7c-14f3127e6c03.overview: Jax takes matters into his own hands as things go sideways.

3602ca43-38ff-4f4a-8f0a-b060a254c30a.overview: Jax brings a new proposal to the club with serious consequences.

6809398a-7b3d-4fa9-bb89-c9e8dfd22c30.overview: Jax attempts to pull Samcro into a new business venture.

c05b50e0-d293-44c4-b600-8f4e3b881877.title: Stolen Huffy
c05b50e0-d293-44c4-b600-8f4e3b881877.overview: Complications arise as the Sons band together to face a new adversary.

501c7534-217f-4442-bf80-ab2e0d9263af.title: Laying Pipe
501c7534-217f-4442-bf80-ab2e0d9263af.overview: A desperate situation tests familial and club bonds.

4675b962-ab3e-4cc6-865c-be06d72f42c4.overview: Set up by Damon Pope and being sought by police, Jax rallies the MC's resources to plan their next moves. Knowing Pope's endgame, Jax seeks Romeo's protection before he, Chibs and Tig end up behind bars as sheep-to-the-slaughter. As Opie struggles to decide his future with the Sons, an unexpected visit from a brother forces the issue.

b21b6558-b3c0-4e91-bc5c-3f79d1705370.title: Sovereign
b21b6558-b3c0-4e91-bc5c-3f79d1705370.overview: Jax presides over SAMCRO as a series of events begin to unravel Charming.

702ec027-55cc-4892-8c44-653e76b07617.title: To Be, Act 2
702ec027-55cc-4892-8c44-653e76b07617.overview: Jax must overcome great obstacles as he attempts to finalize the gun deal between the Irish and the cartel.

bebec20e-8488-4a4e-b984-2a7dfc652be4.title: To Be, Act 1
bebec20e-8488-4a4e-b984-2a7dfc652be4.overview: Jax faces a new challenge that threatens his family and SAMCRO.

6f183998-bca0-439b-9820-f7e5fb79ddcc.title: Burnt and Purged Away
6f183998-bca0-439b-9820-f7e5fb79ddcc.overview: SAMCRO negotiates with the Irish Kings to secure the club's future.

469e2fb4-a9ca-4930-964b-25d2e36549c1.title: Call of Duty
469e2fb4-a9ca-4930-964b-25d2e36549c1.overview: SAMCRO faces a powerful adversary that threatens their business with the Cartel.

6d1ae9d3-adc0-45f7-91d1-8a8572f255a7.title: Hands
6d1ae9d3-adc0-45f7-91d1-8a8572f255a7.overview: Jax and Tara get a glimpse of life without SAMCRO but discover that their reality is hard to escape.

67b230a8-ba27-481a-bdbf-591bee740af2.title: Kiss
67b230a8-ba27-481a-bdbf-591bee740af2.overview: SAMCRO gets word that the Niners have made a new alliance that directly impacts their own agenda.

8a389e7a-6c2c-4b5a-b3d2-c9ddc0e22d20.title: Family Recipe
8a389e7a-6c2c-4b5a-b3d2-c9ddc0e22d20.overview: SAMCRO must put off an important vote to deal with an external threat.

21315f1a-0d40-4216-a1a2-5e3052c72597.title: Fruit for the Crows
21315f1a-0d40-4216-a1a2-5e3052c72597.overview: As Jax searches for who threatened Tara, she becomes aware of what's been going on with the club and warns Jax that Clay can't be trusted.

b34166cb-18c0-474d-9e7e-3a064498b260.title: With an X
b34166cb-18c0-474d-9e7e-3a064498b260.overview: SAMCRO’s relationship with the Cartel is in jeopardy when an important package is compromised.

5e5237eb-ceee-497d-b222-05135c2ab55f.title: Brick
5e5237eb-ceee-497d-b222-05135c2ab55f.overview: SAMCRO enlists a former foe to help stop the advancement of Charming Heights, while the Sheriff presses Juice for more information.

2ea95dc2-38a6-4747-9d24-9ef1761f3268.title: Una Venta
2ea95dc2-38a6-4747-9d24-9ef1761f3268.overview: SAMCRO makes a run to set up a new business venture with their Tucson charter, SAMTAZ while Gemma makes a new ally in town with Police Chief Roosevelt's wife, Rita.

c358400b-4d5f-4a0d-994c-691e790c389e.title: Dorylus
c358400b-4d5f-4a0d-994c-691e790c389e.overview: SAMCRO encounters an unlikely foe when a piece of their business goes missing.

2e9fe004-d7dd-4a82-b3f9-52287391bee7.title: Booster
2e9fe004-d7dd-4a82-b3f9-52287391bee7.overview: After exacting their revenge, SAMCRO is forced to make a decision that could cause a huge shift in the club.

d0418024-b6c2-42ee-888f-4966d5323a8f.title: Out
d0418024-b6c2-42ee-888f-4966d5323a8f.overview: 14 months after going to prison on federal weapons charges Jax, Clay and the other SAMCRO members are released and return to Charming where they encounter new enemies in the form of a no nonsense sheriff and an Assistant U.S. Attorney out to nail the club for their dealings with Russian gunrunner Putlova. Also Jax makes a promise to Tara and Opie and Lyla get married.

bf9779f8-c572-4e5c-a5bc-0ed884eb9d7a.title: NS
bf9779f8-c572-4e5c-a5bc-0ed884eb9d7a.overview: Both the ATF and the Russians prove obstacles as the club looks to heal old wounds.

85605468-5e98-4843-ad5d-797e09161313.title: June Wedding
85605468-5e98-4843-ad5d-797e09161313.overview: With a SAMCRO family member held hostage, Jax must choose between revenge and the good of Charming.

52c9b646-2109-423a-ac36-8bd92b16dcf5.title: Bainne
52c9b646-2109-423a-ac36-8bd92b16dcf5.overview: While the club's on a man hunt, Jax faces the toughest decision of his life.

ae4237da-5236-4852-aaec-c612bd0c68c9.title: Firinne
ae4237da-5236-4852-aaec-c612bd0c68c9.overview: The IRA wants proof that one of their own has flipped and Samcro intends to give it to them.

75ace576-0760-4dd5-a3ac-3329035be840.title: Turas
75ace576-0760-4dd5-a3ac-3329035be840.overview: The club embarks on a protection run, the likes of which they’ve never seen before.

3c0a97f1-58d5-42da-9783-6afc071f14bb.title: Lochan Mor
3c0a97f1-58d5-42da-9783-6afc071f14bb.overview: When SAMCRO pays a visit to another charter, not everyone’s happy to see the mother chapter.

9707ac39-34b2-4801-bcd7-248102b37219.title: Widening Gyre
9707ac39-34b2-4801-bcd7-248102b37219.overview: The Grim Bastards have a problem that could jeopardize Samcro's new business arrangements.

8380eed3-52f2-4226-a9d0-0f34764c1e22.title: The Push
8380eed3-52f2-4226-a9d0-0f34764c1e22.overview: To protect their territory, SAMCRO must handle a rat at St. Thomas.

b4249e57-f5f3-4877-91ea-67d0daf2fef9.title: Turning and Turning
b4249e57-f5f3-4877-91ea-67d0daf2fef9.overview: To help Gemma, SAMCRO and Abel, Jax conspires with an unlikely source. Meanwhile, the MC puts Chucky undercover.

d3df25f9-5a89-4b99-88d8-9567366d1474.title: Home
d3df25f9-5a89-4b99-88d8-9567366d1474.overview: Jax and Clay head towards Canada after Jimmy provides misleading intel on Abel’s whereabouts. The rest of the club splits off to help Happy with a pharmaceutical favor in redneck territory. Gemma tries to put old family matters to rest.

0673d93b-a8f6-4e57-b1fd-af58ba24193c.title: Caregiver
0673d93b-a8f6-4e57-b1fd-af58ba24193c.overview: To secure weapons and raise money for Abel’s search, the club exploits its porn connections to entertain Henry Lin’s clients, which doesn’t sit well with Opie (Ryan Hurst). Jax’s decision to search for Abel in Canada gets derailed. When Gemma’s dad goes MIA, her prisoner makes plans to do the same.

bb847a26-c216-498d-8db8-e2b805bf59bb.title: Oiled
bb847a26-c216-498d-8db8-e2b805bf59bb.overview: To get intel on Abel’s whereabouts, Jax and the club help a bounty hunter track down a skip. They also press a source for answers about the attack at Half-Sack’s wake - the MC way. Meanwhile, Gemma deals with her father’s dementia.

e531580b-a7b3-47cf-b903-edf110e88ced.title: SO
e531580b-a7b3-47cf-b903-edf110e88ced.overview: The aftermath of Abel’s kidnapping has the Sons reeling - especially Jax, whose grief sends him into deeper turmoil over his future with the MC. Framed for murder, Gemma remains on the lam, and is hit with some unexpected news from her past.

81d28b63-4243-4075-af0b-f15a41648c4c.title: Na Trioblóidí
81d28b63-4243-4075-af0b-f15a41648c4c.overview: The second season ends with SAMCRO trying to get rid of Ethan Zobelle (Adam Arkin) and his cohorts once and for all.

f33cf394-9697-45bc-bece-aae45355f5cf.title: The Culling
f33cf394-9697-45bc-bece-aae45355f5cf.overview: Jax and Clay keep SAMCRO focused on their impending showdown with Zobelle's group; thanks to Gemma, Tara improves her job security at the hospital; Weston finally discovers his boss's intentions in Charming.

b730ae1b-9058-420e-a149-3fabf78c486b.title: Service
b730ae1b-9058-420e-a149-3fabf78c486b.overview: While Opie seeks both revenge and reconciliation, Chibs makes a secret deal with Agent Stahl (Ally Walker) to protect his wife and daughter.

a5ee9edd-332c-499e-90aa-0b06c4af00b9.title: Balm
a5ee9edd-332c-499e-90aa-0b06c4af00b9.overview: Agent Stahl (Ally Walker) takes notice at the handsome profits SAMCRO is reaping from the repo business. Meanwhile, the Jax- Clay standoff forces Gemma to make a difficult decision.

f6f7178c-f3ca-468b-bfd0-962ce68158f8.title: Fa Guan
f6f7178c-f3ca-468b-bfd0-962ce68158f8.overview: When SAMCRO's adult-film business becomes a hindrance to the club, Clay seizes the opportunity to revive the gun-running cartel. As Jax and Clay continue to clash over club activities, their relationship reaches a new level of antagonism.

9d902553-e9bf-49cf-8dab-fe8a6e23ad8f.title: Potlatch
9d902553-e9bf-49cf-8dab-fe8a6e23ad8f.overview: Extreme measures are taken by SAMCRO to get a hold of weapons for a customer. A theft at Caracara Studios means revenge after one diva is put at risk. Tara's professional and personal lives begin to collide.

a78fc88b-0df1-4c03-ac9c-592cd378b1dd.title: Gilead
a78fc88b-0df1-4c03-ac9c-592cd378b1dd.overview: Since The League has SAMCRO members behind bars, the club must make new alliances in prison to survive. Alcohol, Tobacco and Firearms Agent Stahl uses this imprisonment to test Jax and Clay's relationship.

afec9baf-28ff-4a2f-be7e-de59462c8f07.title: Faix Cerebri
afec9baf-28ff-4a2f-be7e-de59462c8f07.overview: Zoebelle incites Clay, who plans a course of retaliation, causing Jax to look to an unlikely source to keep the club from being destroyed. Tara learns from Gemma how an old lady handles anger.

b7ef5386-4a0d-441a-b2fc-97b9012b16b6.title: Smite
b7ef5386-4a0d-441a-b2fc-97b9012b16b6.overview: While Jax and Clay lock horns (and line up support) over how to deal with Zobelle, Tara finds herself ensnared in Gemma's emotional struggle in the aftermath of her attack. Meanwhile, SAMCRO gets help from an unlikely source.

67a55e8b-cf12-4798-bfc0-920c45c881c9.title: Eureka
67a55e8b-cf12-4798-bfc0-920c45c881c9.overview: Tensions between Jax and Clay escalate when they disagree over strategy for rescuing Tig after he's captured by bounty hunters on a gun-running mission. Back in Charming, Gemma is rattled by a graphic reminder of her attack, and she sets out to do something about it.

36e379cf-006d-415e-9886-9bcf3e0c2c89.title: Fix
36e379cf-006d-415e-9886-9bcf3e0c2c89.overview: Zobelle comes up with a problem that Hale can solve to frustrate SAMCRO. Meanwhile, Gemma being raped is really affecting her relationship with Clay and the fact that Jax is involved with Luanne's porn business is bothering Tara. Clay decides to give Bobby the responsibility of running the business side of Luanne's.

e2db28d9-1d27-4d73-940d-065c35aa1164.title: Small Tears
e2db28d9-1d27-4d73-940d-065c35aa1164.overview: After Gemma experiences something horrible she can't tell Jax and Clay. A rival porn producer comes to try and put Luanne out of business and Clay doesn't like Jax's decision making.

bc8d8e74-367b-4126-940a-5e03ae44bd55.title: Albification
bc8d8e74-367b-4126-940a-5e03ae44bd55.overview: Donna's death has the club divided, with Clay setting up a new gun deal with the IRA. Charming and SAMCRO 's hold on the city is threatened after Ethan Zobelle a sophisticated separatist opens a tobacco shop. Zobelle and his less-sophisticated associate are determined to take SAMCRO down due to their black and Latino bikers.

a9363511-cb95-434e-b70c-e14cb15302a8.title: The Revelator
a9363511-cb95-434e-b70c-e14cb15302a8.overview: In the wake of a tragedy, the club must re-evaluate its bonds of brotherhood.

a48d86d6-616c-49d6-9d81-a0ae53ba7d39.title: The Sleep of Babies
a48d86d6-616c-49d6-9d81-a0ae53ba7d39.overview: Clay's solution to getting cash for Bobby's defense leaves SAMCRO in a vulnerable position; Abel's happy homecoming ends in turmoil for the club.

462bca78-ce42-4ab0-ad9f-826cf7a6282b.title: Capybara
462bca78-ce42-4ab0-ad9f-826cf7a6282b.overview: Jax's loyalty to SAMCRO is tested when one member is arrested and another disappears. Meanwhile, Abel's improving condition could spur his release from the NICU, but his homecoming may not be the only one.

ae917708-cf28-48af-b11a-c2b50739d488.title: Better Half
ae917708-cf28-48af-b11a-c2b50739d488.overview: With Stahl pressing the women of SAMCRO, Jax sees Unser as the key to salvation; Cherry reveals interesting information about her past.

18b9988e-93bc-4924-9ded-8bf4d61495e6.title: Hell Followed
18b9988e-93bc-4924-9ded-8bf4d61495e6.overview: SAMCRO plans retaliation on a rival biker club while dealing with wounded Cameron Hayes in the clubhouse; Jax, Bobby and Opie try to end the gun debt for good.

c2459feb-f335-413f-b954-4b9140b089cd.title: The Pull
c2459feb-f335-413f-b954-4b9140b089cd.overview: With the IRA gun payment looming, Samcro scrambles to come up with the cash; the Mayans and Nords take a drastic step toward strengthening their alliance; Jax finds himself in a dangerous position with Tara.

ef7b2ae9-0d6f-4d82-8fe6-c74d8bef507e.title: Old Bones
ef7b2ae9-0d6f-4d82-8fe6-c74d8bef507e.overview: When old bones are discovered on the outskirts of Charming, Clay must deal with long-buried secrets; the club sets its sights on prize money in a bare-knuckle brawl; Kohn's investigation becomes personal when his true intentions are revealed.

9a9e53ec-c707-445a-9448-de27616f676d.title: AK 51
9a9e53ec-c707-445a-9448-de27616f676d.overview: A small favor for Piney's old war buddy turns into a big problem for SAMCRO; Gemma deals with the effects of aging.

0b271e27-319d-4978-a20e-bddbf35d3adb.title: Giving Back
0b271e27-319d-4978-a20e-bddbf35d3adb.overview: Gemma hosts a town fundraiser, bringing the former club member responsible for Opie's arrest back to town; Clay deals with protecting a perverse parolee who can lead to a big payoff.

186d37ee-b5f5-43c9-9da4-8865945b722a.title: Patch Over
186d37ee-b5f5-43c9-9da4-8865945b722a.overview: The club travels to Nevada to store arms with a brother club; when the Mayans pose a threat, Clay decides to "patch-over" the tribe, making them an official charter; Tara's ex, an ATF agent, investigates SAMCRO.

3ed28a25-0768-47b4-84a4-5624b350e29a.title: Fun Town
3ed28a25-0768-47b4-84a4-5624b350e29a.overview: When a prominent Charming family's young daughter is assaulted at a carnival, SAMCRO races against the authorities to capture the assailant; a new shipment of guns arrives from the group's IRA connection; Tara's ex-boyfriend arrives in Charming.

904f2e42-3f89-4e79-ad00-42d97f2fefa0.title: Seeds
904f2e42-3f89-4e79-ad00-42d97f2fefa0.overview: As the club deals with the aftermath of its illegal arms warehouse attack, the deputy chief of police poses a new threat to SAMCRO's reign over Charming; Jax continues to worry about his newborn son's fate; Opie faces a difficult decision.

23118464-d985-45d6-9fc9-946329f7c134.title: Pilot
23118464-d985-45d6-9fc9-946329f7c134.overview: When a rival club cleans out and then destroys their illegal arms warehouse, SAMCRO (Sons of Anarchy Motorcycle Club, Redwood Original) executes their own sense of justice in retrieving their guns. Meanwhile, family issues take center stage with a medical emergency involving Jax Teller's newborn son.
